This MOD uses Akismet to block spam posts and registrations in SMF
NOTE: In order to use this MOD, you need to have a WordPress API Key. If you don't have one, please see http://wordpress.com/api-keys/.
Until you enter your WordPress API key (via the SMF Admin Panel, under 'Block Spam'), this MOD will not function.


